t_news_profile_video::title: Profile Video Report
t_news_profile_video::clip_card_11::goal: Ask: Can you please tell us about your future?
t_news_profile_video::clip_card_0::goals: Show us where your character lives.
t_news_profile_video::clip_card_5::goals: Show us the most important thing about your character’s work.
t_news_profile_video::text_card_0::text: This template will help you report on an individual who is important to your community. The clips suggested cover the primary shots you will need to create a well-rounded profile.. Feel free to skip shots, or use different shots as needed. Additionally, adapt the suggested questions to suit your needs.
t_news_profile_video::clip_card_1::goals: Ask: Will you please introduce yourself?
t_news_profile_video::clip_card_8::goals: Show what your character does for fun.
t_news_profile_video::clip_card_9::goals: Show us something important to the character.
t_news_profile_video::clip_card_12::goal: Show your character at the end of the story.
t_news_profile_video::clip_card_6::goals: Show us a place important to your character.
t_news_profile_video::clip_card_2::goals: Show us what you find notable about your character.
t_news_profile_video::clip_card_7::goals: Show your character interacting with other people in their life.
t_news_profile_video::clip_card_3::goals: Ask: Please tell us a little about what you do for a living?
t_news_profile_video::clip_card_10::goal: If it’s a new place, show where your character ends the story.
